API name: BabbleLabs Clear Cloud Unspecified API v0.9.0
Description: The BabbleLabs Clear Cloud API allows developers to utilize speech enhancement for common format video and audio. It provides a way to enhance streaming audio content, upload an audio file to be enhanced, download the enhanced version, upload a video file with embedded audio to be enhanced, download the enhanced version and enhance the audio in the context of a video stream. BabbleLabs files are processed via cloud API in Google Cloud that delivers automated, zero-click speech enhancement processing. This includes the following audio and video formats; wav, mp3, aac, ogg, aiff, mp4 and mov. BabbleLabs is enhancing speech quality, accuracy, and personalization to power voice applications and devices.
